Greetings..

## What is libmcu
We offer what facilitate microcontroller development in four areas:
- Firmware Development
- Development Boards
- Web Application
- Cloud Service

## Ready to get started?
Find out how to build and flash your first firmware with libmcu in [Get
Started](/docs/getting-started). Check out [API Documentation](https://docs.libmcu.org) too.
